{{Quote|Once I was a knight, and now I'm only a [[Fool|fool]]... I may be a fool, but I'm a ''living'' fool, thanks to you.|Ser Dontos the Red, to [[Sansa Stark]]|Two Swords}}
Ser '''Dontos Hollard''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 2|second]] and [[Season 4|fourth seasons]]. He is played by guest star [[Tony Way]] and debuts in &quot;[[The North Remembers]].&quot; Also known as '''Ser Dontos the Red''', he is made a [[Fool|fool]] by King [[Joffrey Baratheon]] after attending a [[Tourney|tourney]] drunk.

